Cell["\<\
Each element is labelled by a pair of Gelfand-Zetlin patterns, the first of \
which corresponds to a standard Young tableau and the second to a Weyl \
tableau.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->736796687,ExpressionUUID->"cba71e28-8ac5-4a14-a64d-3c18c15df125"],

